caption: Bindings
tags: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/profiles
title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/profiles/bindings
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A //binding// is a //template string//.  Each `{{...}}` in it is a //token//
that resolves a path against the current record and substitutes the result.
Anything outside `{{...}}` is literal text:

```
"{{course}}/{{name}}-{{id}}"   ← three tokens, two literal "/" and "-" separators
"text/vnd.tiddlywiki"          ← no tokens, plain literal
"{{message|html-to-wikitext}}" ← one token, piped through a transform
```

See [[Section 6|$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/tokens]] for the full token grammar.
